## Integration

**With gremlin-brain-v2:**
- Auto-runs on activation (φ-tier default)
- Uses Dewey index as ground truth
- Updates fragmentation log in .claude/brain/

**With nexus-graph-visualizer:**
- Uses graph data for loop detection
- Shares coherence data for visualization

**With phase-boundary-detector:**
- Applies boundary analysis at tier interfaces
- Flags where structure breaks at transitions

