## Commands

```
CHECK φ        → Check seed tier (default on activation)
CHECK π        → Check structure tier
CHECK e        → Check current tier
CHECK i        → Check deep tier
CHECK ALL      → Full coherence scan
REGEN [tier]   → Regenerate selected tier
BOUNDARIES     → Check all phase boundaries
ANALYZE        → Run fragmentation pattern analysis
LOG            → Show fragmentation log
REPAIR [issue] → Fix specific issue
```

